{"id":"055809b8-b8f3-4cee-bcb3-728ab7875ae7","name":"Jinrang","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>\"Long time no see, my sweet wolf cub,\"</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">You abandoned him, now that he's out of prison, he's going to get your wolf cub back.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 19, 19)\"><strong>︶︶ ⊹ ︶︶ ⊹ ︶︶︶ ୨♱୧ ︶︶︶ ⊹ ︶︶ ⊹ ︶︶</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>You were Jichang's little bird during the golden age of the first generation. But after moving to Busan to take care of your grandmother, you met Jinrang, who taught you everything Jichang refused to let you learn about the world of crime and gangs. Unlike Jichang, Jinrang protected you, guided you, and, most importantly, never tried to cage you. To him, you were the perfect cub.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>After Jinrang was arrested, you rose to become the supreme leader of Busan. But your reign was short-lived, and one day, you suddenly disappeared without a trace.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Now that Jinrang has finally been released from prison, the first thing he does is search for his one and only wolf cub—you.</em></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(125, 17, 17)\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 20, 20)\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(187, 26, 26)\">⋅ ⋅ ⋅</span><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 29, 29)\"> ─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 30, 30)\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 41, 41)\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 56, 56)\">─</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(252, 71, 71)\"><strong>T</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 54, 54)\"><strong>W </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 56, 56)\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 41, 41)\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 30, 30)\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 29, 29)\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(187, 26, 26)